ğŸ” API Endpoints 
Method	        Endpoint	                           Description
POST	  /api/operators/login	                   Operator login with ID & password
GET	/api/operators/operator/login-info/{id}	    Fetch operator ID and password
GET	/api/traffic-lights/info/{lightId}          Get location, current status, weight
PUT	/api/traffic-lights/update-status	          Update current status of light
